01:03:57,772 --> 01:04:01,647
...Alfredo leaves and goes
to find his mother.

481
01:04:01,772 --> 01:04:05,065
He hadn't seen her for 10 years,
beacause he was lousy.

482
01:04:05,565 --> 01:04:09,315
He hadn't told Ambaro
where his mother lived.

483
01:04:09,607 --> 01:04:13,149
Lots of things going on
in this movie.

484
01:04:13,608 --> 01:04:16,483
But the most important
thing is...

485
01:04:17,150 --> 01:04:21,609
...after years full of
regrets and studies...

486
01:04:22,817 --> 01:04:27,235
...Amparo finds the address
of his mother.

487
01:04:29,402 --> 01:04:32,069
And goes there.

488
01:05:18,243 --> 01:05:21,535
Hotel Youkali.
Room 15.

489
01:05:49,331 --> 01:05:52,748
- Sleep, my darling.
- And what if I be a burden by mistake?

490
01:08:24,271 --> 01:08:26,688
And Alfredo...

491
01:08:29,189 --> 01:08:32,148
...stays inside her...

492
01:08:34,940 --> 01:08:37,398
...for ever.

493
01:08:58,610 --> 01:09:02,819
AFTER ONE MONTH

494
01:09:03,903 --> 01:09:08,070
Come on, put your hands
correctly... This way...

495
01:09:13,862 --> 01:09:17,113
It's quite cool...
It's great...

496
01:09:17,530 --> 01:09:20,655
It's nice here by
the balcony, right?

497
01:09:20,905 --> 01:09:24,114
Lydia likes to sit by
the balcony as well.

498
01:09:24,906 --> 01:09:27,531
Did you hear that? She likes
it a lot.

499
01:09:28,240 --> 01:09:32,532
Look at them... It's as if
they are talking about us.

500
01:09:34,699 --> 01:09:37,116
What do you think they say?

501
01:09:37,866 --> 01:09:40,498
They have no shame.

502
01:09:40,533 --> 01:09:44,034
Women talk about everything
with each other.

503
01:09:45,367 --> 01:09:49,493
Lydia would tell her she has
completed two months sick.

504
01:10:26,415 --> 01:10:28,797
Benjamin and Angela...

505
01:10:28,832 --> 01:10:33,125
...will you bond in marriage,
with your own will?

506
01:10:36,375 --> 01:10:40,168
Join your hands together...

507
01:10:40,543 --> 01:10:44,835
...and declare your wish
in front of God.

508
01:10:49,252 --> 01:10:52,378
I, Angela,
take you, Benjamin...

509
01:10:52,878 --> 01:10:56,170
...to be my lawful husband...

510
01:10:56,545 --> 01:11:00,337
I will love you
in happiness and in sickness...

511
01:11:00,837 --> 01:11:05,088
...so long as we shall both live.

512
01:11:06,380 --> 01:11:09,714
The Lord that joined you in love...

513
01:11:10,005 --> 01:11:14,381
...let him accept your declaration
of love today.

514
01:11:14,798 --> 01:11:18,632
May your love last eternally.

515
01:11:19,215 --> 01:11:22,591
What are you doing here? We
were gonna meet at the hotel.

516
01:11:22,674 --> 01:11:26,883
I changed my mind.
I've always liked weddings.

517
01:11:27,175 --> 01:11:30,592
Weren't you gonna see
your sister before the game?

518
01:11:30,842 --> 01:11:33,891
I called her.
She will come to the hotel.

519
01:11:33,926 --> 01:11:37,260
I promised her we will eat at
the restaurant tonight.

520
01:11:37,295 --> 01:11:39,260
As you wish.

521
01:11:44,219 --> 01:11:48,136
- Nice ceremony, right?
- Excellent.

522
01:11:51,345 --> 01:11:55,513
- I didn't expect her so young.
- You don't trust me right?

523
01:11:56,471 --> 01:11:59,972
We can't have another day
passing by without talking.

524
01:12:00,347 --> 01:12:04,639
Don't worry. Finish with Angela,
I have proof.

525
01:12:05,222 --> 01:12:09,265
For example, at the ceremony
I didn't cry, you did.

526
01:12:09,300 --> 01:12:12,223
- Right.
- And you shouldn't have.

527
01:12:12,390 --> 01:12:14,515
Don't you believe me?

528
01:12:14,807 --> 01:12:19,141
I needed 10 years to get over
it. I finally made it.

529
01:12:21,392 --> 01:12:24,517
Lydia, trust me,
it's over.

530
01:12:25,267 --> 01:12:27,774
I travelled with Angela.

531
01:12:27,809 --> 01:12:31,476
The excuse was to write
a travel guide.

532
01:12:31,851 --> 01:12:36,394
In reality, I wanted her
out of Madrid and drugs.

533
01:12:36,811 --> 01:12:41,228
Madrid is hell. Our relationship
functioned outside it.

534
01:12:42,020 --> 01:12:45,770
After five trips,
I brought her to her parents...

535
01:12:45,805 --> 01:12:50,021
...who kept her away
from drugs and from me.

536
01:12:50,646 --> 01:12:52,771
Did you still love her?

537
01:12:54,438 --> 01:12:58,606
I cried not being able to share
things with her.

538
01:12:59,647 --> 01:13:03,773
It's terrible to leave
a person you love so much.

539
01:13:04,482 --> 01:13:06,774
What a sad story!

540
01:13:07,399 --> 01:13:11,024
Love is a sad thing when
it ends...

541
01:13:11,059 --> 01:13:13,566
...as the song says.

542
01:13:13,941 --> 01:13:16,692
Marco, we need to talk afterwards.

543
01:13:16,983 --> 01:13:21,026
- We've been talking for an hour.
- You have, not me.

544
01:13:21,776 --> 01:13:23,818
You're right.

545
01:13:50,322 --> 01:13:53,656
My leg needs two months of therapy,
said the doctor.

546
01:13:53,989 --> 01:13:57,073
But you know what? I am glad
that bull hit me.

547
01:13:57,531 --> 01:14:00,907
Now I can stay with you until
you wake up.

548
01:14:00,942 --> 01:14:03,449
No one will take me away from you.

549
01:14:05,158 --> 01:14:08,533
We got back together,
a month ago...

550
01:14:09,908 --> 01:14:13,867
Lydia would tell you at the
wedding. She didn't in the end.

551
01:14:16,701 --> 01:14:19,535
It was you she cried for.

552
01:14:21,827 --> 01:14:26,369
She called me to tell me
she cried for me.

553
01:14:27,828 --> 01:14:30,668
Last time we spoke.

554
01:14:30,703 --> 01:14:34,204
Now that I don't fight
due to injury...

555
01:14:34,329 --> 01:14:37,496
...I would like to stay
near her during the night.

556
01:14:37,531 --> 01:14:39,871
Like at your place.

557
01:15:17,669 --> 01:15:20,169
I am alone again.

558
01:15:24,462 --> 01:15:27,052
You were looking at her breasts.

559
01:15:27,087 --> 01:15:30,296
Difficult to avoid it.
They grow by the day.

560
01:15:30,629 --> 01:15:35,297
Benigno, I am thinking of taking
a trip... I have to work.

561
01:15:35,755 --> 01:15:37,880
And Lydia?

562
01:15:38,422 --> 01:15:40,922
She doesn't need me anymore.

563
01:15:42,923 --> 01:15:45,006
Did you break up?

564
01:15:45,965 --> 01:15:48,972
You can call it that way.

565
01:15:49,007 --> 01:15:53,133
I expected this, Marco.
Don't ask why, I just did.

566
01:15:54,716 --> 01:15:59,425
There was something in your
relationship that didn't function right.

567
01:15:59,759 --> 01:16:01,849
When are you going?

568
01:16:01,884 --> 01:16:04,885
Soon, but I'll see you before
I go.

569
01:16:05,176 --> 01:16:07,635
I am so sorry you are going.

570
01:16:12,594 --> 01:16:15,678
I am leaving, Benigno.
I'll see you soon.

571
01:16:18,053 --> 01:16:21,762
She didn't have her period yet?

572
01:16:23,262 --> 01:16:27,388
I am looking at the month's report.
She should have had it.

573
01:16:28,763 --> 01:16:31,222
Yes, it's a bit late.

574
01:16:43,474 --> 01:16:47,516
Two weeks. That's a lot.
Are you sure she had it last month?

575
01:16:48,183 --> 01:16:52,475
I personally dealt with it.
It was when you had the flu.

576
01:16:53,684 --> 01:16:56,059
She seems a bit swollen.

577
01:16:56,476 --> 01:16:58,983
They often have abnormalities.

578
01:16:59,018 --> 01:17:02,435
For example, Lydia
doesn't have a period anymore.

579
01:17:02,935 --> 01:17:06,686
Anyway, we should tell Dr Vega.

580
01:17:25,272 --> 01:17:29,023
I brought some of my guides
for Alicia and you.

581
01:17:30,773 --> 01:17:33,190
I said goodbye to Lydia.

582
01:17:34,773 --> 01:17:39,149
I went to see Alicia, but they
didn't let me enter the room.

583
01:17:41,149 --> 01:17:43,400
Is there something wrong?

584
01:17:43,817 --> 01:17:46,900
No. Just some infection
that Alicia got.

585
01:17:47,109 --> 01:17:50,255
Can you drive me home?
I am done with work.

586
01:17:50,290 --> 01:17:53,366
- It's not serious, I hope.
- I don't know.

587
01:17:53,401 --> 01:17:57,485
They do some medical exams,
but they haven't told me anything.

588
01:17:58,527 --> 01:18:01,659
Brazil...

589
01:18:01,694 --> 01:18:04,028
...Turkey, Cuba.

590
01:18:04,903 --> 01:18:08,112
- I will read them to Alicia.
- They are guides.

591
01:18:08,570 --> 01:18:11,494
Yours. They must be good.

592
01:18:11,529 --> 01:18:14,155
- Are you travelling alone?
- Yes.

593
01:18:14,446 --> 01:18:17,613
I would like to talk to you
about this before you go.

594
01:18:17,947 --> 01:18:21,239
- About what?
- loneliness.

595
01:18:21,406 --> 01:18:23,781
I want to get married.

596
01:18:26,406 --> 01:18:29,573
- Alicia, of course!
- Benigno, you are nuts!

597
01:18:29,608 --> 01:18:32,706
We will get along better than
most couples.

598
01:18:32,741 --> 01:18:36,116
- Why shouldn't I marry her?
- Because she is in a coma!

599
01:18:37,867 --> 01:18:41,575
Because she can't say 'yes'
in the church!

600
01:18:41,992 --> 01:18:45,701
Because, she is virtually dead!

601
01:18:45,736 --> 01:18:47,583
Get in the car!

602
01:18:47,618 --> 01:18:50,160
- What are you talking about?
- Get in the car!

603
01:18:56,411 --> 01:18:59,995
Your relationship with Alicia
is a crazy monologue!

604
01:19:00,287 --> 01:19:03,954
We often talk to PVS,
but we don't marry them.

605
01:19:04,537 --> 01:19:08,538
Incredible what you are saying.
I had a different opinion of you.

606
01:19:08,830 --> 01:19:12,497
Don't say or think about it
ever again!

607
01:19:13,080 --> 01:19:17,873
Promise!... If you say that to
anyone else, you will be in trouble!

608
01:19:20,040 --> 01:19:23,124
If that calms you down,
then I promise.

609
01:19:23,374 --> 01:19:26,541
- Regardless of how much you like her...
- You like her too, right?

610
01:19:26,576 --> 01:19:28,708
Of course I like her.

611
01:19:29,291 --> 01:19:33,229
- She likes you too.
- She is virtually dead!

612
01:19:33,264 --> 01:19:37,167
She has no feelings about me,
you, or herself!

613
01:19:37,202 --> 01:19:39,793
Understand that!

614
01:19:45,002 --> 01:19:48,690
Our patient Alicia Roncero
was raped and is pregnant.

615
01:19:48,725 --> 01:19:52,378
Before I tell her father
I want you to tell me...

616
01:19:52,413 --> 01:19:55,545
...which bastard did it!

617
01:19:55,580 --> 01:19:57,969
Everyone is upset.

618
01:19:58,004 --> 01:20:01,838
You are responsible. Alicia
was on your floor.

619
01:20:02,130 --> 01:20:05,422
Then allow me to explain the
situation.

620
01:20:06,047 --> 01:20:08,339
Rosa, please.

621
01:20:09,547 --> 01:20:13,465
Alicia's period stopped
two months ago.

622
01:20:13,840 --> 01:20:18,007
I thought it was one month
initially, but I was wrong.

623
01:20:18,215 --> 01:20:21,383
It wasn't in last month's report.

624
01:20:21,591 --> 01:20:24,716
It says it was dealt with normally.

625
01:20:24,966 --> 01:20:28,300
I was down with flu
during that week.

626
01:20:29,301 --> 01:20:32,384
You wrote that.
Right, Benigno?

627
01:20:32,634 --> 01:20:35,802
- It is your typewriting.
- Yes, it was me.

628
01:20:36,010 --> 01:20:38,969
Why did you lie?

629
01:20:39,510 --> 01:20:42,017
I didn't want it to become a problem.

630
01:20:42,052 --> 01:20:45,636
On other occasions, the patients'
periods have also stopped.

631
01:20:46,928 --> 01:20:51,054
How come no one noticed?
Where is the night person?

632
01:20:51,262 --> 01:20:54,596
She can't come today.
She phoned.

633
01:20:54,679 --> 01:20:56,895
Didn't see notice anything strange?

634
01:20:56,930 --> 01:21:01,305
She has problems at home.
A lot of nights she doesn't come.

635
01:21:01,556 --> 01:21:04,223
And who replaces her?

636
01:21:07,890 --> 01:21:11,057
I will tell Roncero
that his daughter...

637
01:21:11,432 --> 01:21:14,349
...is day and night with
a nutter?

638
01:21:14,432 --> 01:21:16,683
Lets calm down for a bit.

639
01:21:18,391 --> 01:21:23,642
Benigno, do you realise you
are the prime suspect?

640
01:21:24,559 --> 01:21:27,733
Why did you hide the first delay?

641
01:21:27,768 --> 01:21:32,144
What explanation do you have?
Would you ever harm Alicia?

642
01:21:32,394 --> 01:21:34,352
Definitely not!

643
01:21:39,978 --> 01:21:42,819
Last night I was
at the parkin lot...

644
01:21:42,854 --> 01:21:46,813
...and overheard a discussion
between Benigno and Marco.

645
01:21:46,938 --> 01:21:50,438
Benigno said he wanted to
marry Alicia.

646
01:21:50,855 --> 01:21:54,814
Marco tried to change his mind,
but in vain.

647
01:21:57,731 --> 01:22:00,155
Lots of couples, he said...

648
01:22:00,190 --> 01:22:03,648
...don'r get along
as well as him and Alicia.

649
01:22:05,815 --> 01:22:09,441
AFTER EIGHT MONTHS

650
01:22:25,819 --> 01:22:29,903
It was Lydia Gonzales' funeral
yesterday, at Almudena.

651
01:22:31,111 --> 01:22:36,570
The thirty-year old bullfighter
was in a coma since...

652
01:22:39,737 --> 01:22:42,342
Can I speak with
Benigno Martin?

653
01:22:42,377 --> 01:22:44,947
He doesn't work here anymore.

654
01:22:46,072 --> 01:22:48,405
- Are you sure?
- Positive.

655
01:22:48,780 --> 01:22:51,405
- And sister Rosa Lazaga;
- Who are you?

656
01:22:51,440 --> 01:22:54,031
- Marco Zuloaga.
- I will put you through.

657
01:22:58,532 --> 01:23:01,616
- Who is it?
- Marco Zuloaga.

658
01:23:02,533 --> 01:23:05,700
I am calling from Jordan.
I found out about Lydia.

659
01:23:05,735 --> 01:23:08,242
I am sorry, Marco.

660
01:23:08,909 --> 01:23:11,367
You should have called me.

661
01:23:12,826 --> 01:23:15,326
We had a lot of problems here.

662
01:23:15,576 --> 01:23:18,827
What happened? Benigno isn't
there anymore, I was told.

663
01:23:19,285 --> 01:23:22,452
Benigno is in jail.

664
01:23:25,411 --> 01:23:29,203
He is accused of raping Alicia.

665
01:23:31,745 --> 01:23:34,913
Help him. He has no one
the poor guy.

666
01:23:34,948 --> 01:23:37,003
Did you go see him?

667
01:23:37,038 --> 01:23:39,955
After what he did, I can't.

668
01:23:40,205 --> 01:23:43,497
However he does need help,
and you are his friend.

669
01:23:43,706 --> 01:23:47,206
- What prison is he in?
- In Zegovia.

670
01:24:38,089 --> 01:24:40,714
Wait for me here.

671
01:24:56,134 --> 01:24:59,634
- I want to see a prisoner.
- In the visting section.

672
01:24:59,669 --> 01:25:02,176
Through this door,on the left.

673
01:25:13,470 --> 01:25:16,560
I want prisoner Benigno Martin.

674
01:25:16,595 --> 01:25:19,721
It isn't a visting day,
but I will see whether...

675
01:25:19,756 --> 01:25:21,929
I am sorry, I can't hear you.

676
01:25:23,138 --> 01:25:25,561
It isn't a visiting day.

677
01:25:25,596 --> 01:25:29,555
And the lodger didn't ask
for a visit.

678
01:25:30,055 --> 01:25:33,306
He doesn't know I am in Madrid.
I came today.

679
01:25:33,723 --> 01:25:37,098
- Are you a relative?
- A friend.

680
01:25:37,223 --> 01:25:41,057
- Marco Zuloaga is my name.
- Can I see your I.D.?

681
01:25:43,933 --> 01:25:47,892
- Can I call him?
- He will call you.

682
01:25:48,183 --> 01:25:51,809
I have changed number. Can you
give him the new one?

683
01:26:01,102 --> 01:26:03,192
And remember.

684
01:26:03,227 --> 01:26:06,644
Visiting days are Saturday
and Sunday.

685
01:26:06,978 --> 01:26:10,937
But the lodger should ask for
the visit.

686
01:26:11,229 --> 01:26:14,479
If he doesn't want to see you,
there is nothing we can do.

687
01:26:16,021 --> 01:26:20,147
And something else. We don't
have prisoners here...

688
01:26:21,188 --> 01:26:25,647
We don't have prisoners here,
we have lodgers.

689
01:27:02,570 --> 01:27:04,945
Marco, is that you?

690
01:27:05,862 --> 01:27:10,238
I am glad to hear your voice.
I asked your visit on Saturday.

691
01:27:12,696 --> 01:27:15,030
- Where are you?
- Outside the clinique.

692
01:27:17,197 --> 01:27:21,281
Dr Vega told me everything.
How could you do it?

693
01:27:21,948 --> 01:27:25,198
Did you come back to Spain
to get on my back?

694
01:27:26,532 --> 01:27:29,616
Do you need anything?
What should I bring you on Saturday?

695
01:27:29,699 --> 01:27:33,366
I need information.
What do you know about Alicia?

696
01:27:33,401 --> 01:27:35,700
They wouldn't say anything
from the clinique.

697
01:27:36,033 --> 01:27:38,242
She is in a different one.
They don't know where.

698
01:27:38,367 --> 01:27:41,263
- I don't believe this.
- Neither do I.

699
01:27:41,298 --> 01:27:44,160
But I am not surpised they
won't tell us.

700
01:27:44,451 --> 01:27:48,035
- Are you still my friend?
- Of course. Since I am here.

701
01:27:48,244 --> 01:27:50,536
Then find out about Alicia.

702
01:27:50,952 --> 01:27:54,369
Whether she's alive, whether she gave
birth, whether the baby is alive...

703
01:27:54,578 --> 01:27:58,412
I need to know, Marco...
You understand, right?

704
01:28:00,954 --> 01:28:05,580
I will try to...
Talk to you on Saturday...

705
01:28:07,663 --> 01:28:11,330
- Did you find out anything?
- I will. Be patient.

706
01:28:11,664 --> 01:28:16,998
I was, until the day she would
give birth. One month ago.

707
01:28:17,706 --> 01:28:20,082
You must wait.

708
01:28:26,291 --> 01:28:30,667
- What do you do during the day here?
- I work in the recovery room.

709
01:28:31,417 --> 01:28:36,043
It's a new prison, few people.
It's quiet in here.

710
01:28:36,668 --> 01:28:40,168
- It doesn't look like a prison from outside.
- The problem is elsewhere!

711
01:28:40,627 --> 01:28:43,627
That I don't see Alicia.

712
01:28:44,336 --> 01:28:48,461
The doctor ki o Dr Roncero
say I am a psychopath.

713
01:28:51,920 --> 01:28:55,879
This is good for the trail, they say,
but I don't care about the trial.

714
01:28:56,296 --> 01:29:00,338
I need to see Alicia,
to find out how everything went.

715
01:29:01,005 --> 01:29:05,214
If this goes on, I don't
know what I am capable of doing!

716
01:29:05,464 --> 01:29:07,714
I am a psychopath, they say?
Then I will act like one!

717
01:29:07,749 --> 01:29:09,715
Don't say that, Benigno!

718
01:29:10,923 --> 01:29:15,299
And find me another lawyer.
The one I have despises me.

719
01:29:17,924 --> 01:29:22,133
I will rent my place so that
I can pay him.

720
01:29:22,592 --> 01:29:25,863
I will rent it.
I am currently homeless.

721
01:29:25,898 --> 01:29:29,134
Great. I am glad you will be
my tenant.

722
01:29:29,926 --> 01:29:34,010
I was thinking about you a lot,
especially during the nights.

723
01:29:34,802 --> 01:29:38,302
- Why during the nights?
- Because I study during the nights.

724
01:29:38,552 --> 01:29:41,344
I read all your guides.

725
01:29:41,511 --> 01:29:45,220
Like travelling with you
next to me...

726
01:29:45,255 --> 01:29:47,720
...telling me things.

727
01:29:48,012 --> 01:29:51,179
I liked Avan's the most.

728
01:29:51,429 --> 01:29:53,763
I became one with those people...

729
01:29:53,846 --> 01:29:57,014
...that have nothing
and invent everything.

730
01:29:58,014 --> 01:30:01,181
And you describing
the Cuban girl...

731
01:30:01,216 --> 01:30:04,348
...in front of her window
by the sea...

732
01:30:04,383 --> 01:30:06,473
...waiting in vain...

733
01:30:06,973 --> 01:30:10,182
...for something that will
never happen.

734
01:30:10,807 --> 01:30:13,891
I was thinking that woman is me.

735
01:30:32,644 --> 01:30:35,936
Good morning. I am Benigno's
friend.

736
01:30:36,478 --> 01:30:39,312
You are Marco, the Argentinian?

737
01:30:39,687 --> 01:30:44,521
Benigno called me.
Will you take his appartment?

738
01:30:45,354 --> 01:30:49,772
It will be dirty. He wouldn't
let me in to clean it.

739
01:30:51,272 --> 01:30:55,398
- And I didn't want any money...
- It's OK, I will take care of it.

740
01:30:55,689 --> 01:30:59,482
Shall I give you the key?...
I will go look for it...

741
01:31:06,233 --> 01:31:08,316
Did you see him?

742
01:31:09,441 --> 01:31:12,317
- How is he?
- Well.

743
01:31:13,567 --> 01:31:17,651
Poor guy, he wasn't even lucky
during his imprisonment.

744
01:31:17,686 --> 01:31:19,908
No publicity!

745
01:31:19,943 --> 01:31:24,235
No TV, no reporters.
No one came here.

746
01:31:24,735 --> 01:31:28,028
They didn't condescend!
And they show such garbage!

747
01:31:28,063 --> 01:31:30,195
I would give them an interview!

748
01:31:30,445 --> 01:31:33,070
The media is shit in this country!

749
01:31:33,237 --> 01:31:35,237
You are right.

750
01:31:35,737 --> 01:31:37,862
The keys...

751
01:31:38,446 --> 01:31:43,030
Anyway... Do you know why
Benigno is in prison?

752
01:31:43,488 --> 01:31:47,781
He is very quiet. He didn't say
a word last time he came.

753
01:31:48,364 --> 01:31:51,448
- Benigno is innocent.
- Yes, I know.

754
01:31:51,698 --> 01:31:54,740
- Innocent about what?
- I don't know.

755
01:31:55,115 --> 01:31:58,366
You do, but you don't want
to tell me.

756
01:32:03,533 --> 01:32:07,075
If you need something,
you know where I am.

757
01:34:05,427 --> 01:34:09,386
I was glad you stepped in
by yourself today, without crutches.

758
01:34:11,928 --> 01:34:14,803
- How did the exercise go today?
- Very well.

759
01:34:14,838 --> 01:34:17,019
- Were you tired?
- A lot.

760
01:34:17,054 --> 01:34:20,679
It doesn't matter. We will
do some extra exercises.

761
01:34:21,971 --> 01:34:24,763
We will do some stretches.

762
01:34:25,097 --> 01:34:28,931
- But I already did 100.
- We'll do a few more.

763
01:35:05,978 --> 01:35:08,770
I have an appointment with
Mr. Sainz.

764
01:35:13,271 --> 01:35:16,230
The boy was born dead.

765
01:35:16,355 --> 01:35:19,626
Alicia recovered.
Benigno hasn't found out.

766
01:35:19,661 --> 01:35:22,897
In his condition,
he could do something crazy.

767
01:35:23,356 --> 01:35:27,190
I can't lie to him.
He is my only friend.

768
01:35:27,690 --> 01:35:31,239
I will tell him.
I have no problem.

769
01:35:31,274 --> 01:35:34,941
Alicia is still in coma and
the baby dead, I will say.

770
01:35:35,149 --> 01:35:38,073
But you don't tell him anything.

771
01:35:38,108 --> 01:35:42,900
- Can he bail out?
- Very difficult, and expensive.

772
01:36:11,572 --> 01:36:14,329
- You are wet.
- A little.

773
01:36:14,364 --> 01:36:19,198
Be careful not to catch a cold.
Drink hot milk with honey.

774
01:36:30,866 --> 01:36:34,784
Since I am here,
I like rainy days.

775
01:36:37,409 --> 01:36:40,076
Dld you see the new lawyer?

776
01:36:42,951 --> 01:36:47,077
He was here...
he told me everything...

777
01:36:49,494 --> 01:36:53,161
- I will loose, right?
- Frankly, yes, you will.

778
01:36:53,196 --> 01:36:56,829
At least nothing happened to
Alicia during birth.

779
01:36:57,287 --> 01:37:01,579
It's the only thing that consoles
me and gives me hope.

780
01:37:03,371 --> 01:37:05,663
Are you ok, Benigno?

781
01:37:09,581 --> 01:37:13,206
I would like to hug you
so much, Marco.

782
01:37:14,706 --> 01:37:18,415
But I have to ask for a meeting
face to face.

783
01:37:18,450 --> 01:37:20,541
I tried.

784
01:37:22,083 --> 01:37:25,166
They asked me whether you are
my lover.

785
01:37:25,333 --> 01:37:29,542
I didn't dare say 'yes' since
that would annoy you.

786
01:37:29,792 --> 01:37:34,293
It wouldn't annoy me at all.
You can say whatever you want.

787
01:37:34,626 --> 01:37:38,252
I have hugged very few people
in my life.

788
01:38:33,552 --> 01:38:35,469
Message!

789
01:38:39,595 --> 01:38:43,512
I was very happy to see you
and say goodbye today.

790
01:38:44,387 --> 01:38:47,241
They won't let me get
out of here...

791
01:38:47,276 --> 01:38:50,096
...or they will put me
somewhere else

792
01:38:50,388 --> 01:38:53,103
I don't want to live
without Alicia...

793
01:38:53,138 --> 01:38:56,931
...without being able to hold
not one pin of hers.

794
01:38:57,556 --> 01:38:59,973
Therefore I will escape.

795
01:39:00,264 --> 01:39:04,140
I didn't tell you so that you
won't stop me.

796
01:39:04,307 --> 01:39:06,932
I hug you firmly, Marco.

797
01:39:24,768 --> 01:39:27,810
In Zegovia...
Yes, in prison...

798
01:39:47,897 --> 01:39:51,356
I urgently need to see Benigno Martin.

799
01:39:51,647 --> 01:39:54,731
It's a matter of life and death.

800
01:39:55,023 --> 01:39:58,190
The warden is waiting for you
in his office.

801
01:39:58,225 --> 01:40:00,899
Me? Where is his office?

802
01:40:01,357 --> 01:40:03,983
The guard will accompany you.

803
01:40:11,359 --> 01:40:14,026
Empty your pockets, please.

804
01:40:27,653 --> 01:40:30,070
Wait, don't run.

805
01:40:36,238 --> 01:40:38,238
In there at the end.

806
01:40:39,738 --> 01:40:42,947
Good morning. I am
Marco Zuloaga.

807
01:40:43,614 --> 01:40:47,031
Benigno Martin left this
letter for you.

808
01:40:54,532 --> 01:40:56,789
Dear Marco...

809
01:40:56,824 --> 01:41:00,950
It's still raining, and this
is a good sign.

810
01:41:02,325 --> 01:41:06,034
When Alicia had the accident,
it was raining too.

811
01:41:06,534 --> 01:41:10,284
I am writing to you a few
minutes before I escape.

812
01:41:10,319 --> 01:41:14,035
I hope, with all these,
to fall in a coma as well...

813
01:41:14,070 --> 01:41:16,327
...and to be near her.

814
01:41:17,077 --> 01:41:19,661
You are my only friend.

815
01:41:20,119 --> 01:41:24,078
I am leaving you the house
I prepared for me and her.

816
01:41:25,995 --> 01:41:30,496
Wherever they take me, come to
see me and talk to me.

817
01:41:31,079 --> 01:41:34,955
Tell me everything, without
hiding anything.

818
01:41:35,788 --> 01:41:38,081
Goodbye, my friend.

819
01:41:56,000 --> 01:41:59,917
I took these from him and these
I found at his cell.

820
01:42:08,835 --> 01:42:11,211
You must sign here.

821
01:42:20,629 --> 01:42:22,837
Benigno, it's me.

822
01:42:25,380 --> 01:42:29,922
Alicia is alive...
You woke her up.

823
01:42:33,672 --> 01:42:38,006
I got your message and ran
immediately to tell you...

824
01:42:38,257 --> 01:42:40,799
...but it was too late.

825
01:42:40,924 --> 01:42:44,507
I put a pin of Alicia
in your pocket.

826
01:42:46,549 --> 01:42:49,217
And a photo of hers.

827
01:42:50,008 --> 01:42:53,134
And a photo of your mother.

828
01:42:54,009 --> 01:42:57,426
So that they can be with you
in eternity.

829
01:44:22,481 --> 01:44:26,232
Like wild waves. The male on top,
the female below.

830
01:44:26,565 --> 01:44:28,274
I will bring some water.

831
01:44:57,570 --> 01:44:59,570
Are you ok?

832
01:45:02,529 --> 01:45:04,571
I don't know...

833
01:45:07,071 --> 01:45:09,530
I am much better now.

834
01:45:22,824 --> 01:45:25,366
Come on, lets go inside.

835
01:45:30,575 --> 01:45:32,659
You tremble.

836
01:45:34,325 --> 01:45:35,867
Why?

837
01:45:47,244 --> 01:45:49,703
- What did you tell her?
- Noting.

838
01:45:49,738 --> 01:45:51,752
I saw you talking.

839
01:45:51,787 --> 01:45:55,287
She asked if I am ok, and I
thanked her.

840
01:45:57,204 --> 01:46:01,830
You will see me around.
I live near the dancing school.

841
01:46:02,580 --> 01:46:05,539
In Benigno's place?

842
01:46:06,164 --> 01:46:09,706
- Why do you stay there?
- Benigno is dead.

843
01:46:14,957 --> 01:46:18,249
One day, we should talk.

844
01:46:18,582 --> 01:46:22,166
Yes, and it will be simpler
than you thought.

845
01:46:22,500 --> 01:46:24,583
Nothing is simple.

846
01:46:25,000 --> 01:46:28,209
I am a dancing teacher, and nothing is simple.
and nothing is simple.

